His Excellency, The Former Vice President Of The Federal Republic Of Nigeria, Alhaji Atiku Abubakar Was spotted With Governor Bala, Senator Rabiu Kwankaso and Dino Melaye at Nnamdi Azikwe, Abuja.
It will be recalled that the gentlemen were in the capital city of Abuja to participate in the recent Area Council Elections Hold In FCT.
The polls, conducted to elect council chairmen and councillors, were held in Abaji, Bwari, Gwagwalada, Kuje, Kwali, and Abuja Municipal Area Council (AMAC).
Speaking earlier today, Atiku wished all the PDP leaders present during the election exercise a safe journey back to their various destinations.
He also pray for God Almighty grant them success in the coming 2023 general elections in Nigeria.
